query:
INSERT INTO auth_sessions (user_id, session_secret_hash)
            VALUES ($1, $2)
            RETURNING
                id                  AS "id!",
                user_id             AS "user_id!: Uuid",
                session_secret_hash AS "session_secret_hash?",
                created_at          AS "created_at!",
                last_used_at        AS "last_used_at?",
                revoked_at          AS "revoked_at?"
